'Do you guys think it was wrong of TMZ or do you appreciate that they gave the world the news as soon as they got it!? '

TMZ is like any other media house reporting on news in real time, I doubt the staff at the media house were trying to be insensitive (or I hope not).  We are living in an age of fast news, fast food etc so sadly, things like this will occur.

We need to stop being hypocrites, we share and receive all kind of tragedies from our cell phones without considered, all families matter.
